50:19.886 --> 50:22.845
-He put a fucking Glock
to my head.
-A glock?

50:23.716 --> 50:26.110
Yes, sir. Saw it written
right on the side.

50:26.197 --> 50:28.982
Had a shiny pearl handle grip.
It--

50:29.069 --> 50:32.333
Oh, yeah?
Did it have any engraving in it?

50:32.420 --> 50:34.814
You know on that...
shiny pearl handle.

50:34.901 --> 50:36.685
Yes, sir. Yeah, it did.

50:36.772 --> 50:38.992
