and pulled back the handle.

50:46.217 --> 50:47.696
[Nicotra]
Wait, they put it in your mouth?

50:47.783 --> 50:49.481
I thought you said
they put in to your head.

50:49.568 --> 50:52.440
Look, he put it to my head,
then in my mouth.

50:52.527 --> 50:55.139
All right? Then the crazy
son of a bitches start arguing

50:55.226 --> 50:56.836
about which one's
gonna get to pull the trigger.

50:56.923 --> 50:58.359
-Holy shit!
-Mmm!

50:58.533 --> 51:00.144
Put it in your mouth,
and pulled it out...

51:00.231 --> 51:02.276
Man, I swear for God,
can you believe that shit?

51:02.363 --> 51:03.582
[Frank] No.

51:05.671 --> 51:07.020
No, I don't.

51:09.675 --> 51:10.937
Who are you?

51:15.550 --> 51:17.422
You ever heard
of the Pinocchio effect?

51:19.598 --> 51:21.643
The pokey no fect?

51:22.383 --> 51:24.690
No, no. [laughs]

51:25.604 --> 51:27.214
Pinocchio.

51:27.432 --> 51:31.175
You know, the cute wooden puppet
that wished he was a real boy?

51:31.697 --> 51:34.047
Every time he told a lie,
his nose would grow.

51:34.134 --> 51:35.831
Man, I told you.
I swear for God.

51:35.918 --> 51:38.007
What do I have to gain
from lying to you?

51:38.095 --> 51:40.227
You see, Edwin...
Mind I call you Edwin?

51:40.314 --> 51:41.489
You see...

51:41.968 --> 51:45.667
The Pinocchio effect is
when someone's lying,

51:45.754 --> 51:47.060
they know they're lying

51:47.234 --> 51:49.062
So they're working
as hard as they can

51:49.149 --> 51:51.064
to convince you,
that they ain't.

51:51.499 --> 51:53.849
They start babbling,
and going on...

51:53.936 --> 51:57.157
Start spitting out more details,
more words, than necessary.

51:57.244 --> 51:58.898
You know, shit like,

51:58.985 --> 52:01.248
'Do you think I'd lie
about something like that?'

52:01.901 --> 52:03.903
Or, 'What do I have to gain,
lying to you all?'

52:03.990 --> 52:05.383
Whoa.

52:05.905 --> 52:08.168
