I'm lying about?

52:08.777 --> 52:10.257
[Frank] Everything.

52:11.258 --> 52:15.349
For one, a Glock's
a polymer pistol. It's plastic.

52:16.176 --> 52:17.786
You can't add grips to it.

52:17.873 --> 52:19.919
Especially no pearl handle ones.

52:20.833 --> 52:24.793
And, second, it's a striker
fire, hammerless--

52:24.880 --> 52:27.492
Which means there's no hammer
to pull pack on, dumbass.

52:27.883 --> 52:29.407
-[grunts]

52:30.147 --> 52:31.539
[Nicotra]
What the fuck is wrong with you,

52:31.757 --> 52:33.150
you about to have a stroke
or something?

52:35.326 --> 52:37.545
I have neither the time
nor the crayons

52:37.632 --> 52:39.243
to explain all this to you.

52:39.852 --> 52:41.854
But, I'm gonna give it a go,
anyway.

52:43.290 --> 52:44.813
What you're unaware of is,

52:44.900 --> 52:47.033
earlier this afternoon,

52:47.120 --> 52:48.687
those crazy sons of bitches,

52:48.774 --> 52:51.559
that you supplied the intel
and the boards to,

52:51.646 --> 52:54.083
pulled a North Hollywood
shootout.

52:54.954 --> 52:59.045
