smart?

54:18.951 --> 54:21.040
He was just--
all about business.

54:21.127 --> 54:22.650
He wanted
to know the details.

54:22.737 --> 54:24.304
Very specific about the details.

54:24.391 --> 54:25.653
And the mean one?

54:27.176 --> 54:28.613
Oh, oh, he was bad news.

54:31.616 --> 54:33.966
You know, some wild eyes.

54:34.053 --> 54:36.621
He's the type of guy
that's lookin' for any excuse

54:36.708 --> 54:39.667
to hurt someone.
All right? He told me,

54:39.754 --> 54:41.843
