had a Saint Jude pendant
around his neck.

55:00.340 --> 55:01.428
And, uh...

55:03.038 --> 55:07.086
the mean one had a...
Marine corps tattoo.

55:07.173 --> 55:10.959
It said Semper Fi,
it had writin' on it.

55:11.656 --> 55:13.179
What did the tattoo say?

55:15.877 --> 55:18.619
