on the bottom,

55:18.706 --> 55:21.056
-And, then, Sheridan somethin',
on top.
-Say what?

55:21.143 --> 55:24.146
-It said Semper Fi
on the bottom.
-No no no... the name

55:24.233 --> 55:26.845
Oh, uh, Sheridan Raid,
or something.

55:26.932 --> 55:29.064
