about no headquarter branch

55:53.872 --> 55:55.961
and no Thursday deposit either.

55:56.048 --> 55:58.267
Yeah, yeah.
Okay, send me that, right now.

55:59.660 --> 56:01.270
[cell phone beeps]

56:02.489 --> 56:05.318
-This them?
