from the sandbox.

56:33.259 --> 56:35.435
All right, get a bulletin
to all of our agencies.

56:35.522 --> 56:38.220
-And get these photos
to the media ASAP.
-Copy.

56:38.307 --> 56:40.092
-Any word on the bank employees?
